Ab aap yahan par different npm install commands try kar sakte hain.

Try 1: Specific cloudinary version install karein:

Agar aapko pata hai ki cloudinary ka koi specific version multer-storage-cloudinary@4.0.0 ke saath compatible hai, toh aap woh version directly install karne ki koshish kar sakte hain.

Build command:

Bash

npm install cloudinary@1.41.0 && npm install
(Yahan par 1.41.0 ek example version hai. Aapko woh version try karna hoga jo ^1.21.0 ke range mein ho aur available ho.)

