Save Changes aur Deploy Karein: Jab aap sabhi zaroori files mein API URLs ko update kar dein, toh apne changes ko save karein aur apne frontend code ko Render par phir se deploy karein. Kyunki yeh static site hai, aapko Render dashboard se apni frontend service ke liye manual deploy trigger karna pad sakta hai ya aapki deployment settings ke according automatic deploy ho jaega.

Main strongly recommend karunga ki aap ek BACKEND_API_URL constant apne app.js ya kisi common file mein define karein aur phir us constant ko apne saare API calls mein use karein. Isse future mein URL change karna aasaan ho jaega.

Apne frontend code mein yeh changes karne aur deploy karne ke baad, aapki website ko ab aapke backend API se communicate karna chahiye aur login, signup, feedback submit, aur fetch functionalities kaam karne chahiye. Agar ab bhi koi issue aata hai toh apne browser ke "Network" tab aur Render backend logs ko check karna na bhoolen.


