})
.then(response => response.json())
.then(data => {
  // ...
});
Aapko apne code mein is tarah ki calls dhoondhni hain aur ensure karna hai ki URLs sahi hain.

Agar aapko koi specific API call milti hai jismein aapko shak hai, toh us code snippet ko yahan share karein, aur main usko dekhkar bata paunga ki kya problem ho sakti hai.

